3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses AI techniques for facial expression analysis. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing facial expressions in multimedia data. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing facial expressions, which is an important aspect of human-computer interaction.
